  <h2>1. How Can LifeLabs Help Me Maximize the Use of Streaming?</h2>
  <p>-Lifelabs encourages students to cooperate and interact with their peers which can boost their confidence and can be helpful in the future. Boost in confidence can be helpful if someone were to be in a situation where they need to do public speaking or simply a live stream. With confidence and support from their peers they'll be able to be a better version of themselves and move forward.
</p>
